  * Yellow curved block in middle
  * Two orange cylindrical blocks at bottom
- Right configuration:
  * Red curved block on top
  * Blue cube in middle
  * Green rectangular block at bottom
  * Orange cylindrical block on side
  * Small yellow cube on top

1. Blue cube (index 3)
2. Yellow curved block (index 12)
3. Orange cylindrical blocks (index 11)
4. Red curved block (index 1)
5. Green rectangular block (index 5)
6. Yellow small cube (index 4)

Assembly Instructions:
{
   Step1: Move block with index 11 (orange cylinder)
   Step2: Move block with index 11 (second orange cylinder)
   Step3: Move block with index 12 (yellow curved block)
   Step4: Move block with index 3 (blue cube)
   Step5: Move block with index 1 (red curved block)
